{"tid":1492750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"驕兵必敗 哀兵必勝","createTime":"2019-08-21T03:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T04:11:46.000Z","uid":28946,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"02288b48e36b3ef80ad622f12a6f60817cff5d92","tid":1492750,"uid":28946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:22:59.000Z","msg":"革命由六月開始 我明白大家可能好攰 中共用盡一切方法扶黑同淡化 好多不公義嘅事發生咗 我地過咗無數咁多以淚洗面嘅晚上 有人以死明志黎提醒我地 有大量手足被拉 但求下你地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好放棄 唔好習慣 唔好忘記 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地要令革命日常化 airdrop文宣個啲唔講啦講到臭 但我最想講嘅係連登嘅post 仲係唔太多人用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong>不推文回復</strong></strong></strong></strong></span> 令到重要post沉底 版面充斥着冇用唧資訊。 連登未去我地贏之前都係一個好<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重要</span>嘅資訊板 <br />\n<br />\n 最後，唔好一兩次戰役所謂成功咗就算 我地面對嘅對手一日唔回應 我地一日都冇贏過 。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n大家加油<br />\n<br />\n用不推文回復唔重要post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔識用不推文呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2e003752dcdd518e1003f8e31ae58509a8526b","tid":1492750,"uid":38784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89caeea7a2fb52398ef0e4786bf3c22f63412324","tid":1492750,"uid":2142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:27:58.000Z","msg":"推左先"},{"pid":"f0805ac08e63aa03f3b22e85f55d4397e29a2ae0","tid":1492750,"uid":196861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:29:10.000Z","msg":"回<span style=\"color: red;\">覆</span>"},{"pid":"e196eb768a2c6eab19b4d5145a707231e1ccee0e","tid":1492750,"uid":28946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:11:24.0